Slash Featuring Myles Kennedy and the Conspirators - Living the Dream Tour captures the band‚Äôs incendiary performance on their sold-out 2019 tour, in front of a rabid crowd at London‚Äôs legendary Hammersmith Apollo. This will be released on DVD+2CD, Blu-ray+2 CD, 3LP Black Vinyl, limited edition 3LP Red Vinyl, digital video and digital audio, on September 20th 2019.
Living The Dream Tour features Slash & Co. roaring through a highly charged 2-hour set of tracks from all four Slash solo albums. The set includes ‚ÄúCall of the Wild‚Äù ‚ÄúDriving Rain‚Äù, ‚ÄúBy The Sword‚Äù, ‚ÄúBack From Cali‚Äù, ‚ÄúStarlight‚Äù, ‚ÄúWorld On Fire‚Äù and ‚ÄúAnastasia‚Äù. There‚Äôs a searing live version of ‚ÄúShadow Life‚Äù, as well as ‚ÄúWe Are All Gonna Die‚Äù and ‚ÄúDoctor Alibi‚Äù, during which Myles Kennedy switches vocal duties with bassist Todd Kerns.
Slash tears up Hammersmith Apollo with staggering solos while dropping giant slabs of riffs with casual ease, delivering the essence of rock ‚Äòn‚Äô roll in this show. You could see it, hear it and feel it. ‚ÄúEvery night is chasing that magic and when it happens, it‚Äôs euphoric,‚Äù Slash states. ‚ÄúI just love it‚Ä¶London kicks ass‚Äù.
